{"route":{"route":"/posts/88967b7c/","outputPath":"posts/88967b7c/index.html","kind":"post","title":"OpenCV瞳孔定位","language":"zh-Hans","params":{"abbrlink":"88967b7c"}},"description":"利用OpenCV自带的分类器识别面部及眼睛 OpenCV自带里许多分类器,可在haarcascades下载 获取面部 获取眼睛 瞳孔定位 获取的眼睛图像 裁剪去除眉毛 伽马矫正提高图像对比度 转化为灰度图像 利用threshold进行阈值操作(此处可能会改为inRange,目前还在测试) 腐蚀 膨胀 medianBlu","post":{"kind":"post","sourcePath":"source/_posts/OpenCV瞳孔定位.md","route":"/posts/88967b7c/","abbrlink":"88967b7c","title":"OpenCV瞳孔定位","date":"2020-02-06 18:15:35","updated":"2020-02-06 18:15:35","tags":["C++","OpenCV","archlinux"],"categories":["Computer Graphics"],"language":"zh-Hans","htmlLang":"zh-Hans","locale":"zh_CN","textDirection":"ltr","dateLocale":"zh-CN","excerptMarkdown":"","excerptHtml":"","bodyMarkdown":"","bodyHtml":"<h2 id=\"利用opencv自带的分类器识别面部及眼睛\">利用OpenCV自带的分类器识别面部及眼睛</h2>\n<p>OpenCV自带里许多分类器,可在<a href=\"https://github.com/opencv/opencv/tree/master/data/haarcascades\">haarcascades</a>下载</p>\n<h3 id=\"获取面部\">获取面部</h3>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-cpp\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 获取面部</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">// image 为输入的OpenCV的格式的图像</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">// out 为输出图像 &lt;- 此处输出图像为裁剪下来的矩形面部图像</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-type\">bool</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">get_face</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">(cv::Mat image, cv::Mat &amp;out)</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"></span>{</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 将图像转为灰度图像,可提高识别精度</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    cv::Mat gray;</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">8</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    cv::<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">cvtColor</span>(image, gray, CV_BGR2GRAY, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>);</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">9</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 此处的rect为用来存储识别出的面部的定位 &lt;- 这里为vector是因为识别的面部可能不止为一个</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">10</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    std::vector&lt;cv::Rect&gt; rect;</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">11</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 初始化OpenCV的分类器</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">12</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    cv::CascadeClassifier cas = cv::<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">CascadeClassifier</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;haarcascade_frontalface_default.xml&quot;</span>);</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">13</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    cas.<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">detectMultiScale</span>(gray, rect, <span class=\"hljs-number\">1.15</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">5</span>);</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">14</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 判断rect是否为空,为空的话就是没有被识别的面部</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">15</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (rect.<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">empty</span>())</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">16</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">17</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>;</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">18</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    }</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">19</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 输出图像,这里的rect可能不止为一个(因为可能不止一张脸),所以实际中应该使用for循环</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">20</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 我这里用rect[0]为了简化</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">21</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    out = <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">image</span>(rect[<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>]);</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">22</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>;</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">23</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">}</span></span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"获取眼睛\">获取眼睛</h3>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-cpp\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 这里与上面相同(这里我只识别左眼,OpenCV还提供了其他文件可获取右眼和双眼)</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-type\">bool</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">get_left_eye</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">(cv::Mat image, cv::Mat &amp;out)</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"></span>{</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 之后与面部相同</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    cv::Mat gray;</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    cv::<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">cvtColor</span>(image, gray, CV_BGR2GRAY, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>);</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    std::vector&lt;cv::Rect&gt; rect;</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">8</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    cv::CascadeClassifier cas = cv::<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">CascadeClassifier</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;xml/haarcascade_lefteye_2splits.xml&quot;</span>);</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">9</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    cas.<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">detectMultiScale</span>(gray, rect, <span class=\"hljs-number\">1.15</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">5</span>);</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">10</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (rect.<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">empty</span>())</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">11</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">12</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>;</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">13</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    }</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">14</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    out = <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">image</span>(rect[<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>]);</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">15</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>;</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">16</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">}</span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"瞳孔定位\">瞳孔定位</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>获取的眼睛图像</li>\n<li>裁剪去除眉毛</li>\n<li>伽马矫正提高图像对比度</li>\n<li>转化为灰度图像</li>\n<li>利用threshold进行阈值操作(此处可能会改为inRange,目前还在测试)</li>\n<li>腐蚀</li>\n<li>膨胀</li>\n<li>medianBlur平滑图像</li>\n<li>检测关键点并画在图像上</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-cpp\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 定位眼球 -&gt; 检测关键点</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-function\">std::vector&lt;cv::KeyPoint&gt; <span class=\"hljs-title\">dector</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">(cv::Mat image)</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"></span>{</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    cv::SimpleBlobDetector::Params detector_params;</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    detector_params.filterByArea = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>;</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    detector_params.maxArea = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1500</span>;</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    cv::Ptr&lt;cv::SimpleBlobDetector&gt; blob_dector = cv::SimpleBlobDetector::<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">create</span>(detector_params);</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">8</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    std::vector&lt;cv::KeyPoint&gt; keypoints;</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">9</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    blob_dector-&gt;<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">detect</span>(image, keypoints);</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">10</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> keypoints;</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">11</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">}</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">12</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">13</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-type\">bool</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">get_pupil</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">(cv::Mat image, cv::Mat &amp;out)</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">14</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"></span>{</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">15</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// width -&gt; image.rows ;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">16</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// height -&gt; image.cols;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">17</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// cut eyebrow 裁剪 去除眉毛</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">18</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    image = <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">image</span>(cv::<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Rect</span>(image.cols / <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>, image.rows / <span class=\"hljs-number\">2.5</span>, image.cols * <span class=\"hljs-number\">8</span> / <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>, image.rows / <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>));</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">19</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">20</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Gamma correction/gamma nonlinearity 伽马校正 -&gt; https://www.cnblogs.com/sdu20112013/p/11597171.html</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">21</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-function\">cv::Mat <span class=\"hljs-title\">look_up_table</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">256</span>, CV_8U)</span></span>;</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">22</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    uchar *p = look_up_table.<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">ptr</span>();</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">23</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-type\">float</span> gamma = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.7</span>;</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">24</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-type\">int</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>; i &lt; <span class=\"hljs-number\">256</span>; ++i)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">25</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        p[i] = cv::<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">saturate_cast</span>&lt;uchar&gt;(<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">pow</span>(i / <span class=\"hljs-number\">255.0</span>, gamma) * <span class=\"hljs-number\">255.0</span>);</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">26</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    cv::<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">LUT</span>(image, look_up_table, image);</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">27</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">28</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    cv::Mat gray;</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">29</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 转化为灰度图像</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">30</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    cv::<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">cvtColor</span>(image, gray, CV_BGR2GRAY, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>);</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">31</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 阈值操作</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">32</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    cv::<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">threshold</span>(gray, gray, inRange_threshold, <span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, CV_THRESH_BINARY);</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">33</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//膨胀及腐蚀</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">34</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    cv::<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">erode</span>(gray, gray, cv::<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Mat</span>(), cv::<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Point</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">-1</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">-1</span>), <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>);</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">35</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    cv::<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">dilate</span>(gray, gray, cv::<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Mat</span>(), cv::<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Point</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">-1</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">-1</span>), <span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>);</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">36</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 平滑图像</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">37</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    cv ::<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">medianBlur</span>(gray, gray, <span class=\"hljs-number\">5</span>);</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">38</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 检测并画出关键点</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">39</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    cv::<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">drawKeypoints</span>(image, <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">dector</span>(gray), image, cv::<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Scalar</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>), cv::DrawMatchesFlags::DRAW_RICH_KEYPOINTS);</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">40</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    out = image;</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">41</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>;</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">42</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">}</span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"附录\">附录</h2>\n<h3 id=\"opencv在archlinux上的使用\">OpenCV在ArchLinux上的使用</h3>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">pacman -S opencv</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\"># vtk和hdf5为opencv的依赖,不安装编译会失败</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-built_in\">sudo</span> pacman -S vtk</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-built_in\">sudo</span> pacman -Ss hdf5</span></span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"cmake文件\">Cmake文件</h3>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-cmake\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">cmake_minimum_required</span>(VERSION <span class=\"hljs-number\">3.14</span>)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">project</span>(eyedector)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">add_definitions</span>(-std=c++<span class=\"hljs-number\">11</span>)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\"># 这里只需要添加OpenCV的就能编译成功</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">find_package</span>(OpenCV REQUIRED)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">link_libraries</span>(<span class=\"hljs-variable\">${OpenCV_LIBS}</span>)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">add_executable</span>(out opencvtest.cpp)</span></span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"利用安卓手机充当网络摄像头\">利用安卓手机充当网络摄像头</h3>\n<p>手机安装这个<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.pas.webcam\">IP Webcam</a>,使用时会显示局域网中的地址</p>\n<p>OpenCV中</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-cpp\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-function\">cv::VideoCapture <span class=\"hljs-title\">cap</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;http://192.168.0.xx:8080/video&quot;</span>)</span></span>; <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 这里为网络摄像头的地址,需要在后面加上/video</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">while</span> (<span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">{</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    cv::Mat frame;</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    cap &gt;&gt; frame;</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    cv::<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">imshow</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;test&quot;</span>, frame);</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (cv::<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">waitKey</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>) == <span class=\"hljs-number\">27</span>)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">8</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">9</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">exit</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>);</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">10</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    }</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">11</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">}</span></span></code></pre>\n","rawMarkdown":"","plainText":"","toc":[{"id":"利用opencv自带的分类器识别面部及眼睛","text":"利用OpenCV自带的分类器识别面部及眼睛","level":2},{"id":"获取面部","text":"获取面部","level":3},{"id":"获取眼睛","text":"获取眼睛","level":3},{"id":"瞳孔定位","text":"瞳孔定位","level":2},{"id":"附录","text":"附录","level":2},{"id":"opencv在archlinux上的使用","text":"OpenCV在ArchLinux上的使用","level":3},{"id":"cmake文件","text":"Cmake文件","level":3},{"id":"利用安卓手机充当网络摄像头","text":"利用安卓手机充当网络摄像头","level":3}],"slugForSearch":"88967b7c","comments":true,"math":false,"mermaid":false}}